text:
The Resistance: Entertainers say it’s time to throw President Trump in the white van, nullify election Posted at 9:50   William A.   
We here at Twitchy follow a number of Twitter accounts, from news to sports to entertainment. And Hollywood and entertainers have been very vocal about Trump and his presidency, both on stage and on social media. 
This is a collection of Monday tweets from various celebrity and entertainer accounts and the opposition to President Trump: 
— Rosie Perez (@rosieperezbklyn) February 7, 2017 This photo of #PresidentBannon and his toy is too cute https://t.co/kngEa6z5XF
